{{--
    A single line: a Telegram file_id or a public URL. Nothing else — the whole
    file is the value, and it is never escaped.

    $file_id comes from the data you pass to the view, e.g.
      BotResponse::view('receipt', ['file_id' => $id])

    Reuse a file_id returned by Services\MediaUploader::upload() to avoid
    re-uploading the same file on every send.
--}}
{{ $file_id }}
